display_button_left.on('click',e=>{
  //increment down
  i=i-1
  if(i<0){
      i=url.length-1
  }
  display_image.set({url:url[i]})
  display_image.set({'link':links[i]})
  feature.set({'link':links[i]})
  
  
    console.log("i: "+i)
    console.log("url: "+url[i])
    console.log("links: "+links[i])
  
  
})
  


display_button_right.on('click',e=>{
  //increment up
  i=i+1
  if(i==url.length){
      i=0
  }
  display_image.set({url:url[i]})
  display_image.set({'link':links[i]})
  feature.set({'link':links[i]})

    console.log("links: "+links[i])
